title: Green Lantern - New Guardians (000 - 033 + Annuals) (2011 - Ongo
description:
Green Lantern - New Guardians (000 - 033 + Annuals) (2011 - Ongoing) (Digital) (Empire)


A "New 52" initiative book, starring Green Lantern Kyle Rayner leading a team with members from all the Lantern Corps, including Bleez, Arkillo, Munk from the Indigo Tribe, Fatality, Saint Walker and possibly Larfleeze.

With the rising of the third army, created by the Guardians of the Universe, who plot to destroy the lantern corps, Kyle must channel all the ring colors, so he can put up a fight and save them.
